# Generated test fixtures — none are committed. The synthetic marker clip
# (tools/gen_test_media.sh) and the real-clip matrix (tools/gen_clip_matrix.sh:
# clips + the matrix.list / matrix.json manifests) are all regenerated on demand
# by CI and locally. The generator scripts are the single source of truth.
tests/fixtures/
# The demo's copy of the synthetic clip (see demo/README.md) is generated too.
demo/synthetic.mp4
demo/synthetic.mp4.uid

# Headless smoke test project generated artifacts
tests/headless-smoke/synthetic.mp4
tests/headless-smoke/synthetic.mov
tests/headless-smoke/synthetic.m4v
tests/headless-smoke/**/*.uid
tests/headless-smoke/*.uid
tests/headless-smoke/bin/
